ALSUBAIE;Khalifa;Mohd;Turki;;;;01/01/1965;;;Qatari;00685868 (Qatari). Issued in Doha on 5 Feb 2006. Expiring on 4 Feb 2011.;Identity card 26563400140 (Qatari);;;;;;;Doha;;Qatar;UN Ref QI.A.253.08. Qatar-based terrorist financier and facilitator who has provided financial support to, and acted on behalf of, the senior leadership of Al-Qaida, including moving recruits to Al-Qaida training camps in South Asia. In Jan 2008, convicted in absentia by the Bahraini High Criminal Court for financing terrorism, undergoing terrorist training, facilitating the travel of others to receive terrorist training abroad, and for membership in a terrorist organization. Arrested in Qatar in Mar 2008. Served his sentence in Qatar and has been released from detention. Name of mother is Hamdah Ahmad Haidoos.;Individual;AKA;Al-Qaida and Taliban (Al-Qaida);16/10/2008;10/02/2010;10747

DJAMAAT HOUMAH AL-DAWAH AL-SALAFIAT;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;Algeria (western);UN Ref QE.D.102.03. A branch of the Armed Islamic Group (GIA) formed as a result of the break that occurred in 1996 when Afghanistan veteran Kada Benchikha Larbi decided to oppose the head of GIA. As at 1999 the group was led by Mohammed Benslim. Yaha Djouadi subsequently made DHDS part of the Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb. Estimated in Nov 2007 to comprise approximately 50 members.;Entity;AKA;Al-Qaida and Taliban (Al-Qaida);18/11/2003;10/02/2010;7883
